The Artist raised his shield and blocked the shots, but he didn't see Sniper
shoot them. The Artist looked around for Predacons or Alliance but seen
none.

"I'm being fired at, so if you would kindly inlist me?" The Artist said. The
Artist called Liono on his commlink.

"I understand that your the leader, I wish to join you, I have been sent by
the Matrix." The Artist said into his commlink to Liono. Artist continues
his wait outside. Plintissa walks out of the base, but stopped crying when
she seen this bot's eyes. Plintissa knew that this was Suukie. Plintissa
took him closer to the base, the autoguns didn't fire upon him.

"Suukie?" Plintissa asked.

"I never saw you before in my life, my name isn't Suukie, Suukie does not
exist." Artist said. The last words were what made Plintissa realize it,
Suukie didn't remember her anymore. Plintissa held back her tears and walked
into the bases meadow. Dracona looked at Suukie.

"Well, you have the same spark scan as Suukie, so your him." Dracona said,
scanning Artist's spark.

"I've never heard of Suukie before." Artist said, still standing his
position....
